overview: ModaKupi, the largest fashion shopping mall online in Russia, offers over 100,000 branded clothing garments from hundreds of famous brands, such as coats, dresses, lingerie, swimwear, shapewear, jackets, jeans, trousers, pants, shorts, tops, blouses, t shirts, skirts, suits, sweaters, tops, shoes, boots, trainers, slippers, swimwear, bags, clutches and accessories including belts, gloves, hats, scarves and watches for women. ModaKupi shopping marketplace offers unique and friendly product search by color, brand, price and the latest discounts from the top merchants. Brands include Calvin Klein, Clarks, Diesel, Just Cavalli, Fossil, Furla, DKNY, Armani, Hush Puppies, Merrell, Lacoste, Adidas, La Redoute Creation, Anne Weyburn, Laura Clement, Marmot, Burton, Guess, Nike, Puma, Reebok, Salomon, The North Face, Quelle, Miss Sixty, Replay, Gant, BonPrix, Sara Kelly, Mexx, Next, Champion, Lee, Tommy Hilfiger, Wrangler, Esprit, Woman Withing, True Religion, 3Suisses, Speedo, Triumph, Shirley of Hollywood, Ugg, Rieker, Rider, Skechers, Ugg, Hugo Boss, Braccialini, Chantal Thomass, G-Star Raw and many more. The company is based in Moscow, Russia.
